cat
(defsource x [int64 int64])
----
ok

cat
(defsource y [int64 int64])
----
ok

build
(join
  [(get x)
   (filter
     (join [(get x) (get y)] [[#0 #2]])
     [#1])]
   [[#0 #2]])
----
Join on=(#0 = #2)
  Get x
  Filter #1
    Join on=(#0 = #2)
      Get x
      Get y

build apply=JoinFusion
(join
  [(get x)
   (filter
     (join [(get x) (get y)] [[#0 #2]])
     [#1])]
   [[#0 #2]])
----
Filter #3
  Join on=(eq(#0, #2, #4))
    Get x
    Get x
    Get y

